type: software
title: "CLARK — Claude Language Assessment Research Kit"
authors:
  - family-names: "Liu"
    given-names: "Sha"
abstract: >-
  Integrity-first Claude Code skills for language assessment / applied
  linguistics research: automated Zotero-to-Word citations, retraction-checked
  reference audits, a living literature review with a standing radar,
  pre-submission manuscript review, and writing polish. The AI operates the
  workflow and checks the record; the scholar keeps the judgement calls.
